data.description: IDEALLY SITUATED AT THE CORNER OF LOCATION & VALUE!!! Start your new year off right in the family-oriented swimming pool Heritage Hills community!!! Spacious floor plan designed & built with a strong focus on quality of life, oversized master suite with well-equipped ensuite bath & loads of closet space, oversized eat-in kitchen with ceramic tile flooring and custom backsplash, stainless, stove, microwave & fridge, LVP flooring, new carpet, and covered grilling porch overlooking the private fenced back yard. This is a must see in the sought after Long Cane /Troup High school zone!!! $3,500 dollar interior paint allowance paid to the painter of buyers choice at closing!!!
